Name: SyncGo Desktop Calendar
About the game: SyncGo Desktop Calendar (former Desktop iCalendar) is a Powerful and Flexible Calendar App for Windows. It can sync Google Calendar, Office365 Calendar, iCloud Calendar on your Windows desktop, help you to check the events and to-do list at a glance, so that you will never miss important things in your life.
